# =============================================================
# ACTUAL BUDGET — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit the .env file — only .env.example
# Shared variables (ROOT_DOMAIN, DOCKER_DATA_PATH, TZ)
# come from root .env
#
# Actual Budget requires no environment variables to start.
# On first access at https://actual.eirdom.homes you will be
# prompted to set a server password.
#
# Set a strong server password and save to password manager.
# This password is required every time a new device connects.
